title: Baked Ziti
directions: Preheat oven to 350. Prepare a 3 1/2-quart dish with cooking spray; set aside. In a mixing bowl, combine spaghetti sauce, cottage cheese, pasta, half the mozzarella cheese, salt, and black pepper. Mix well. Spread mixture into prepared pan. Sprinkle top with remaining mozzarella cheese and Parmesan cheese. Bake for 30 minutes, or until heated through.
ingredients: 16 oz. ziti pasta, cooked and drained
8 oz. shredded part skim mozzarella cheese, divided in half
